## ğŸš€ Installation

### Prerequisites
- Ensure you have [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) installed on your system.

### Steps to Install
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Maharshi-24/Compliance-Forms.git
cd Compliance-Forms

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the development server
npm run dev

# For production
npm start
```

