## ğŸ“– Usage

1. **ğŸ”‘ Login / Sign Up**: Users must log in to access the system.
2. **â¬†ï¸ Upload Policy**: Uploaders can submit new policies through predefined forms.
3. **ğŸ‘€ Review Policy**: Reviewers evaluate policies and take actions (Approve, Reject, Request Revisions).
4. **ğŸ“š View Policies**: Viewers can access approved policies.
5. **ğŸ“¥ Extract Data**: Users can download policy details in XLSX format.

