## ğŸ‘¥ User Roles & Permissions

| **Role**     | **Permissions**                                                                 |
|--------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Viewer       | Can view approved policies.                                                     |
| Uploader     | Can create and submit policies for review.                                      |
| Reviewer     | Can approve, reject, or request revisions for policies.                         |

